					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4605700#post-3663227</guid>
				<title>This Author Commentary is rocking out to Trans-Siberian Orchestra</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4605700/scp-3882#post-3663227</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2017 19:26:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ihp</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1267048</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>A sequel to <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2217">SCP-2217</a> AND a new Skip? It truly is a Christmas miracle!</p> <p>This started out as a joke post I made <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-3172288/groups-of-disinterest#post-3573811">here</a>, but I eventually looked at it and thought &quot;Yeah, this could work.&quot; Plus, I've wanted to do a follow-up to 2217 for a while, and it's only&#8230; three years late. The lyrics for the songs were the hardest part, as I really don't listen to metal often; apparently, most of the sound of metal comes from the music, and not the lyrics, so at least there's that.</p> <p>Thanks to all my beta readers, including <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1514249734" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/renasanse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2753490&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1514249734" alt="Renasanse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2753490)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/renasanse" >Renasanse</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1514249734" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1514249734" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" >taylor_itkin</a></span>. Have a Merry Christmas, Happy New Year, and Praise MEKHANE.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
